  "text": "As an on-going work, we consider to incorporate the concept of near-clique, which is a clique except for one edge, for computing frequent itemsets into our framework. This may help tolerate the noise in forming a clique in the MI graph. Other measures of inter-dependence [CITATION_1] in the context of QAR mining also deserve attention as a future work.",
